reviewText:
It is informative and well-presented, though old (filmed many years ago).
The film"s title is different from "Meteorite Impact", which I also ordered.
"Meteorites Menace From the Sky & Witness From Beyond the Times" is the same
repeat the same
two movies on one cassette as "Meteorite Impact" on two cassettes.
If I had known they were the same I would have bought one title but not the other.
